snippet.title: Twitter Mob Gets Comic Book LEGEND Frank Miller CANCELLED from UK Comic Convention!
snippet.description:
Salty comics pros on Twitter got legendary Dark Knight creator Frank Miller CANCELLED from Thought Bubble UK by harassing them endlessly. The convention issued an overly dramatic apology, but it's not enough for the Twitter cancellation mob. Now Thought Bubble is "problematic" for even entertaining the thought of bringing in Miller... one of the most popular comic book creators of ALL TIME.
